- This is an Expo React Native project targeting iOS first, Android second
- Use TypeScript strictly throughout
- Use Supabase for all backend interactions
- Use expo-notifications for all push notification scheduling
- Never suggest bare React Native solutions when an Expo SDK equivalent exists
- UI should be minimalist: no unnecessary components, muted palette, clean typography
- All new features should include error handling and loading states
- Follow this folder structure: /app (screens), /components, /hooks, /lib (supabase client, twilio helpers), /types
- Always use LF line endings in all generated files